track_notes: From the Road D27 where you must park. Do no drive on the track, this is forbiden and the fine is 135 Euros.The walk is very easy, it must be some snow in winter time. for the last slope you must climb some very easy rocks. just follow the yellow paint on rocks. The landscape is wonderfull.
track_title: Shortest and easiest track to Mont Brune

track_notes: This forest road is not allowed, but you can enjoy the walk to the summit. Take some water in summertime; plenty room for antenna on top, and nice panorama
track_title: Dont drive on the forest road
